title: Lovely
subTitle: The life of a young woman takes a drastic turn when her parents meet with an accident. Circumstances force her to leave her lover and marry an adulterer eventually ruining her life.

subTitle: A young man misses his bus while on his way to a job interview. The story explores the idea on both counts; what would happen if he gets the bus and what would happen if he misses it.
